⸻

1. Description of the App

NanoBeacon Sensor App is a companion application designed for use with InPlay IN120 compatible wireless temperature sensor hardware.

The App:
	•	Scans for nearby IN120 sensors using Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) advertising packets
	•	Displays temperature and battery data broadcast by compatible devices
	•	Operates in BLE observer (scan-only) mode
	•	Does not establish a traditional BLE GATT connection with sensors

The App requires compatible IN120 hardware to provide live temperature data.

⸻

2. Hardware Requirement

Live sensor readings are only available when:
	•	An IN120-compatible temperature sensor is powered on and nearby
	•	Bluetooth is enabled on your iOS device
	•	Required Bluetooth permissions are granted

If no compatible hardware is present, the App may display “No device found” or similar messages.

⸻

